dct_description_sm: Title in banner held by angels.
Bird's eye view of St. Quentin
Shows the battle of St. Quentin, and the siege of Philip II in August 1557.
Shows fortified camps (tents, artillery), armies (labeled by leader), horses.
dct_subject_sm: Saint-Quentin, Battle of, Saint-Quentin, Aisne, France, 1557
